HEADWORD: Strikeout
<hw>Strike"out</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Baseball)</fld>
<def>an out made by a batter against whom three strikes were called in a
single at-bat; also, the same out as credited to the pitcher, in the
scoring of the game.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

